content:
Aadyaachaaryathvam kaikko-
Baharon mooshayodonnich
Skariyaaykkathu nalki mooshaa
Sariyaa yohannaaneki;
/tyohannaan kartthaavinnum;
/tkartthaa than shleehanmaarkkum;
Naanaasrshdivibhaagangallkkeki shleehanmaar.

Aachaaryathvam mun nirtthi shlee-haril mumpan
Sheemonodu naathhan chonnori-naadam hrdyam;
“ninne grhanaayakanaakki-tthanneedunnen
Ambaradharani'bandhanamukthitthaa-kkolukall; 'nee
/tbandhichaal-nyaanum bandhikkum;
/tmochichaal-mochikkum nyaanum;
Paapikalle prathi abhyarththhichennaal-ketteedum'.

Sleebaa vennu; vellunnu;
Sleebaa vidveshiye vennu;
Sleebaaye saakshichorkkaayu
Sleebaayaakatte kotta.
